name: The Oracle of La Ferla Manor
description:
One of the three maidens of La Ferla Manor. The Oracle is a visionary psychic. She's a loner, often feared. People are intimidated by the strange and unknown. But she is very kind and helpful to those brave enough to approach. When people relinquish themselves to her, they begin to understand her amazing beauty and willingness to give. 

Shot on location at the home of Dominic La Ferla in Torrance, California.

See the body painting in motion at: https://youtu.be/0h8dMkSCsIE

model: Ulorin Vex
body paint and photography by: Roustan (bodypainter.com)
